        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;filter:blur(5px);">Arm holding reported higher-than-expected <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #6b705c; color: black;" href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-06-02-2025-h2-3-third-quarter-earnings?source=website" target="_blank">third-quarter earnings</a>. However, the company’s cautious forward guidance led to a drop in the stock price in after-hours trading. Arm has been one of the major beneficiaries of the surge in AI demand. The company designs chips that are used in smartphones and data centers. Its stock rallied nearly 35% in 2025, outperforming other semiconductor stocks.
          </p>
